---
title: Cozy Daal-Style Coconut Lentil & Shrimp Stew with Grilled Cheese Toasties
description: This vegetarian curry cooked in coconut cream is deeply satisfying on a cold winter's night. Put down the spoon and use the melty cheese toasties to scoop up every last drop of deliciousness!
